---
title: Mini Turkey Meatloaves with Orange Cranberry Sauce
description: Classic and comforting (even a little old-school), our individual meatloaves are done in no time and as delicious as they are fun. Served with a zingy orange-cranberry sauce, they have all the retro Sunday dinner vibes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/petits-pains-de-viande-a-la-dinde-bf9b5b1b.jpg
